last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 1
last_episode_to_air.overview: In this episode, Sebastian Yatra, who always sleeps with socks on, performs "No Hay Nadie Mas" and "Robarte un Beso"; Natti Natasha, who doesn't know how to swim, performs "Dutti Love" and "La Mejor Version De Mi"; plus, Juanes performs "La Camisa Negra" and "Island in the Sun"; and Jackie Cruz performs "Melly 16" and covers Amy Winehouse's "Valerie."

name: HBO Latino Presents: A Tiny Audience
original_name: HBO Latino Presents: A Tiny Audience
overview: In this series of intimate music specials, Latin musicians reveal a personal secret to the "tiny" audience before them and perform a pair of songs that are meaningful to them.
